T\uc0\u7893  ch\u7913 c ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n l\'e0 g\'ec?
\b0 \
T\uc0\u7893  ch\u7913 c ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n (CA) l\'e0 nh\u7853 n d\u7841 ng s\u7889  x\'e1c nh\u7853 n ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n v\'e0 l\'e0m cho ch\'fang tr\u7903  th\'e0nh t\'e0i li\u7879 u \u273 i\u7879 n t\u7917  h\u7907 p l\u7879 . V\'ec b\u7843 n th\'e2n CA l\'e0 c\'e1c nh\u7853 n d\u7841 ng s\u7889  n\'ean ch\'fang c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t CA kh\'e1c x\'e1c nh\u7853 n, t\u7841 o th\'e0nh c\'e1i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7885 i l\'e0 \'93chu\u7895 i ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n\'94. \u272 \u7875  ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n tr\u7903  th\'e0nh h\u7907 p l\u7879 , CA x\'e1c nh\u7853 n ph\u7843 i h\u7907 p l\u7879  v\'e0 c\u7913  nh\u432  v\u7853 y trong chu\u7895 i. Vi\u7879 c n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh t\u7921  \u273 \u7897 ng b\u7903 i ph\u7847 n m\u7873 m h\u7879  th\u7889 ng khi \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 m\u7897 t ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n.\
\

\b T\uc0\u7841 i sao ph\u7843 i \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 c\'e1c ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n?\

\b0 S\uc0\u7917  d\u7909 ng Tr\u7907  l\'fd ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n \u273 \u7875  \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 t\'ednh h\u7907 p l\u7879  c\u7911 a ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n v\'e0 x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh xem c\'f3 ch\'ednh hi\u7879 u kh\'f4ng. Ph\u7847 n m\u7873 m b\u7843 o m\u7853 t, nh\u432  Safari ho\u7863 c Mail, \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 c\'e1c ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n tr\u432 \u7899 c khi s\u7917  d\u7909 ng. V\'ed d\u7909 : n\u7871 u b\u7841 n s\u7917  d\u7909 ng Safari \u273 \u7875  mua th\u7913  g\'ec \u273 \'f3 tr\u7921 c tuy\u7871 n, Safari \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n c\u7911 a trang web v\'e0 cho b\u7841 n bi\u7871 t ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n c\'f3 h\u7907 p l\u7879  kh\'f4ng. Tr\u7907  l\'fd ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n cung c\u7845 p nhi\u7873 u chi ti\u7871 t v\'e0 cho b\u7841 n nhi\u7873 u quy\u7873 n ki\u7875 m so\'e1t h\u417 n \u273 \u7889 i v\u7899 i vi\u7879 c s\u7917  d\u7909 ng c\'e1c ch\u7913 ng nh\u7853 n.}